@FPLFocal That #FBL 🇩🇪 is a far more interesting and fun game. Way more routes to points, five transfers per week, three star players, automatic substitutions.

#FPL 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿 is only interesting if you’re on a Wild Card, and given the numbers playing, if you’ve a dodgy start, the season’s over.
@BenDinnery That’s typical. I just brought Eddie into my #FPL team before his price rise. I hope he’s okay for the weekend.

@hailcheaters Hi Josh and Brandon. You ask: “Who’s at fault - the game or people like us who continue to play the game?

For me it’s the game. There are so few ways to points, or free transfers. That’s why over the last three seasons I’ve gotten much more interested in #FBL 🇩🇪 than in #FPL 🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿.
